            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Problem 1. A random walker moves on the lattice "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\mathbb { Z } ^ { 2 }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "according to the following rule: in the first step it moves to one of its neighbors with probability "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "1 / 4"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ", and then in step "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "n > 1"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "it moves to one of the neighbors that it didn’t visit in the step "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "n - 1"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "with equal probability. Let "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "T"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "be the time when the random walker steps on a site that it already visited. Please show that the expectation of T is less than 35. "
                    }
                ]
            },
            "bbox": [
                139,
                235,
                890,
                322
            ]
        },
        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
